## 👨‍💻 About Me

🔹 **Who I Am:** A self-driven student from Sri Lanka passionate about cybersecurity and software development.  
🔹 **Expertise:** Specializing in <strong>HTML</strong> and <strong>Node.js</strong> to create secure, innovative solutions.  
🔹 **Mission:** Outsmart cyber threats, secure systems, and explore the frontiers of ethical hacking.

