## 🌌 Ongoing Projects

### 🚀 Galaxy Base API Service  
- **Tech:** Node.js, RESTful Architecture  
- **Description:** A high-performance API service designed for scalability and security, powering data-driven apps with real-time features and advanced authentication.  
- **Status:** In development—optimizing endpoints and security protocols.

### 🤖 Zai AI Model  
- **Tech:** Node.js, HTML (Frontend)  
- **Description:** An AI-driven model focused on cybersecurity, tackling anomaly detection and threat analysis with interactive web interfaces.  
- **Status:** Experimental phase—refining algorithms and UI integration.

